{"tid":1872832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"AXA頂峰區1200人開大會仲要唔准戴口罩","createTime":"2020-02-10T09:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T09:32:58.000Z","uid":261702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a65dfb584e2c9eeb79d73bec0cb0e47c0381688","tid":1872832,"uid":261702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"一手料<br />\n<br />\n呢個時勢仲要1200人一齊開大會<br />\n呢個時勢仲要chur生意叫人約客傾單<br />\n呢個時勢仲要開會唔比戴口罩<br />\n名副其實戴左都要除番落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔出席<br />\n一係比醫生紙叫做請病假<br />\n一係放低$100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當有1/4人會寧願放低$100<br />\n咁公司一日就咁賺左$30,000<br />\n另類發國難財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奉勸大家如果有AXA agent想約你傾保險<br />\n仲要係<span style=\"color: red;\">頂峰區</span><br />\n請大大力拒諸門外<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：朋友做AXA頂峰區訴苦"}]}